DESCRIPTION:Category: Yoga\nInstructor: Lex B.\nFlow with your breath. Vinyasa classes ignite inner fire\, improve cardiovascular fitness\, make the spine more supple\, and develop total-body coordination. A wide variety of poses link breath and movement\, combined with sun salutations and standing postures.We look to provide all of our students with a quality experience. To help us meet that goal and secure your spot\, you are strongly encouraged to register before the start of class.\nhttps://portal.movementgyms.com/portland/programs/vinyasa-flow?course=U2Vzc2lvbjoxMzAyNzY4ODI=&date=2026-07-02
